# Review

Trigger artifact and implementation review for the active governed change.

## Invocation
```bash
slipway review
```

## Contract
- Evaluates artifact completeness and implementation quality.
- Produces review findings with required/optional layers.
- Show review summary to user with pass/fail per layer.
